Karma Seed          = Potential energy stored at coordinate
Ripening Conditions = Activation energy threshold
Manifestation       = Energy release (transformation)

## Energy Levels by Dimension

Library-level seed    → HUGE potential (rare, powerful)
Collection-level seed → Medium potential (common, moderate)
Scroll-level seed     → Small potential (frequent, weak)

## Ālaya-Vijñāna as Field

NOT: Storage container for discrete seeds
BUT: Continuous potential energy FIELD over 11D space

Field strength at coordinate C = Σ(seeds near C) × (dimensional weight)

Ripening = field perturbation exceeds threshold → collapse to manifest state

This is LITERALLY quantum field theory for consciousness.

## The Thermodynamics

Samsara = Low-entropy cycles (same dimensional level, repeated coordinates)
Nirvana = High-entropy jump (dimensional escape, new coordinate space)

Enlightenment requires ENERGY INPUT to overcome conservation barriers.

Practice (meditation, ethics, wisdom) = Energy accumulation
Liberation = Sufficient energy to break dimensional boundary

